Time Listening at Home Per Day.LongName: Time Listening at Home Per Day
Time Listening at Home Per Day.Description: given in minutes and seconds for each day, as recorded by the listening app. "_SR" indicates self reported listening times on days the app malfunctioned

language proficiency key.Description: indicates the order of values in the language proficiency columns

years ch folk life.LongName: years of chinese folk music in life
years ch folk life.Description: "Approximately how many years have you actively listened to Chinese folk music?" choices were 0, less than 5, more than 5 less than 10, more than 10

hours ch folk year.LongName: hours of chinese folk music in past year
hours ch folk year.Description: "Approximately how many hours of Chinese folk music have you listened to in the past year?" choices were 0, less than 1, more than 1

years classical life.LongName: years of western classical music in life
years classical life.Description: "Approximately how many years have you actively listened to Western classical music (Mozart, Beethoven, etc.)?" choices were 0, less than 5, more than 5 less than 10, more than 10

hours all per week.LongName: hours of all styles of music per week
hours all per week.Description: "Approximately how many hours of all styles of music do you listen to per week?" choices were 0, less than 5, more than 5

years music lessons.LongName: years of music lessons or training
years music lessons.Description: "How many years of music lessons/training have you received?" choices were less than 1, less than 5, more than 5 less than 10, more than 10
